en_227483_0	Senior Member of the Ramanya Maha Nikaya, Chief incumbent of the Getambe Raajo-Pavanaa-Raamaya Venerable Keppetiyagoda Siriwimala Thera says that he condemns those who attack media freedom while also campaigning on the pretext of protecting media freedom.
en_227483_1	This was issuing a special statement over media suppression carried out targeting HIRU.
en_227483_2	Meanwhile, Opposition Leader Mahinda Rajapaksa also condemned the actions against HIRU.
en_227483_3	Mudslinging posters had been put up around Colombo recently against HIRU and the Police are currently carrying out an investigation in that regard.
